      "comment": "LAMORNASCRUFFLES (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.92) in an A6 at this track. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. MAKEIT DYLAN (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 27.97 beating Choices Mile. Has a strong record from box 2, including two wins. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. BALLYCLEARY BELL (4) found the going tougher last start when finishing 4th over 270m at this track. Won an easier race the start before that at this track. Should be about the mark. MISS MONACO (1) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
